Title: Dalan Pure Olive Oil Soap, 150g X 5 pcs.(750 g)
Description: Olive oil has been used for centuries to moisturize and gently cleanse the skin. Its antioxidant properties are legendary for nourishing skin and fighting the signs of aging.Dalan d'Olive 100% Pure Olive oil soap is a long lasting hard bar, with low lathering ability. Rich in vitamin E and antioxidants, it stimulates new cell generation, slows the progression of wrinkles, and gives skin a youthful look.Olive oil soaps offer a pleasant, fruity aroma, rather than an overtly perfumed scent that can irritate sensitive noses. You encounter free radicals every day as you expose yourself to food, pollution, pesticides and chemical beauty products. These free radicals damage cells, potentially causing disease and accelerating aging.Olive oil is a natural source of the antioxidants vitamins E and A, which fight free radicals -- and the benefits are there regardless of whether the oil is ingested or rubbed into the skin in the form of soap.Olive oil also contains oleocanthal, a compound touted for its anti-inflammatory benefits.Olive oil soap cleans your skin without stripping away the natural oils -- so you don't end up dry and flaky after it's use.Olive oil also allows the skin to sweat and shed cells naturally thereby reducing the acnes and skin rashes problems; commercial soaps that contain synthetic cleaners and fragrances can block your pores and cause irritation. Olive oil soap is considered to be the best remedy for dry skin as it helps to exfoliate dead cells and flaky skin. Its moisturizing properties help to soften the skin texture, leaving you with beautiful glowing skin.Another great advantage of using olive oil soap is that it helps in reducing scars and dark spots. Regular use of olive oil soap will help you get rid of those ugly looking marks, making your skin look clean and nourished. Produced from 100% olive oil with 70 years of experience, d?Olive Olive Oil Soap is a natural cleanser for your skin and hair. Its high vitamin E and Antioxidant content nourishes, moisturizes and provides natural softness as it cleans. Our olive oil soap, which can also be used as solid shampoo, is effective against excess oil on scalp, dandruff and hair loss. Upon continual use, it will strengthen and add shine to your hair.

Title: Corioliss Glamour Wand Purple Zebra Hair Curler
Description: Bring on the razzmatazz and glamour with the help of this Corioliss Glamour Wand Purple Zebra Hair Curler. This curler comes with several features which allow you to curl and style your hair without much hassle. Conical Ceramic Barrel Equipped with a conical ceramic barrel, this hair curler allows you to create a variety of hairstyles like soft curls, waves and tight curls. As this barrel comes with a ceramic coating, you will be left with smooth and sleek hair at the end of the process. Adding to this, the ceramic coating leaves your hair frizz-free. This barrel leaves you with natural looking curls. Negative Ion Conditioning Technology The negative ion conditioning technology of this curler emits negative ions which help contain the static electricity in your hair and reduce the frizz. Furthermore, this technology seals the cuticle layer of your hair and facilitates the retention of moisture and natural oils. Title: VibeX CK-102S ® 1.7" LCD Display Automatic Wrist Watch Style Bp Monitor
Description: Whether you’re someone undergoing medical treatment for a condition, or just trying to keep your health in check, one of the fastest ways to monitor yourself is through your blood pressure and pulse rate. Naturally, staying on the normal blood pressure and pulse rate means good news, but such indicators can also be used to determine the efficiency or non-efficiency of a treatment and medication. Have the VibeX CK-102S Blood Pressure Monitor Wrist Type Auto Heart Beat Rate Pulse Meter on hand for accurate readings whenever you need it.This compact, lightweight wrist monitor provides accurate readings in a convenient size. It comes with an automatic memory function that records the last 90 measurements in groups for efficient tracking. Last 3 Results Average feature, meanwhile, automatically calculates the average readings stored. This blood pressure monitor also has an Irregular Heart Beat detector that automatically alerts you when heart rhythm is 25 % faster or slower than the average rhythm detected during the measuring process.This digital blood pressure monitor uses the oscillometric method of measurement--it detects your blood's movement through the brachial artery and converts the movements into a digital reading. This method does not need a stethoscope, making the VibeX CK-102s Automatic Blood Pressure Monitor easier to use. It measures systolic, diastolic, and pulse at the same time.While this device can measure both blood pressure and heart beat, these are completely different and have no correlation. Blood pressure is the force the heart exerts against the walls of arteries as it pumps blood to the body, while pulse is the number of times your heat beats in a minute. Just because your pulse rate is high, doesn’t mean your blood pressure increases too, and vice versa.Always remember that prevention is better than cure.

Title: Glowing Buzz Combo of 1 Natural Anti Tan Pack for Face, Dark Under Arms and Hands, 1 Nourishment Vitamin E Oil and Jojoba Essential Oil
Description: Get even skin tone and reduce tan with this Natural Anti Tan packs from the storehouse collection of Glowing Buzz. It is made out kolin clay, oat and other natural lightening agents that will lighten the skin with no chemicals. Mix optimum amount with papaya or rose water to make a paste and apply all over the face or Under arms or hand. Massage gently for two minutes. Leave it for ten minutes for maximum results and rinse it with water. Follow with Glowing Buzz Herbal Nourishment Vitamin E oil. Apply one to three drops all over the face and massage lightly in an upward direction for two to five minutes or till it get absorbed for a smooth skin. To reduce dark circles apply one to two drops around the eyes and massage gently for two to three minutes every night. Get extremely soft and smooth lips by mixing one drop with malai and massage for two minutes and for shiny hair mix four to six drops in your head massage oil or mask and massage it for ten minutes. Jojoba Oil From The House Of Glowing Buzz Is Known To Have Anti-Bacterial And Anti-Inflammatory Properties. This Makes It Effective In Dealing With The Microorganisms That Attack The Skin Surface And Also With Inflammation That May Develop Due To Injury In The Underlying Skin Layers. Regular Use Of Jojoba Oil Can Therefore Help Keep Skin Healthy And Free From Problems. Jojoba Oil Has Many Organic And Mineral Ingredients, Which Gives A Wonderful And Nicely Groomed Skin. It Helps To Fight Facial Lines, Skin Scarring And Fatty Tissue. It Is Also Efficient On Challenging Skin Circumstances Like Acne. Jojoba Oil Reduces Annoyed Skin And Improves The Natural Development Of Collagen. It Also Offers Efficient Protection Towards Sun. Jojoba Oil Can Also Be Used As A Moisturizer Before Make Up Or As A Make Up Remover Or As A Hair Serum As Well. Just Apply 2-3 Drops Of Glowing Buzz Jojoba Oil As Hair Serum For Shiny And Healthy Hair. Use Only 1 -2 Drops Glowing Buzz Jojoba Oil With Any Moisturizer To Get A Glowing Skin.
